title: RQ: Porcupine Tree & Riverside (Dutch Treat Symphonic Indie)
description:
On request, my two favorite Symphonic Indie Rock Bands.

Another change to ask some extra attention for Riverside. They do not get the attention they deserve. There are a few million people out there, that really love this music and do not know it yet. A few hundred uploads is hardly enough. So really try it, you wont be disappointed...... Enjoy,
